These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, palace
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, zombie, comedy
There are 3 different nationalities: british, pakistani, colombian
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, dancer, software-developer
3 different games are played: whist, canasta, snooker
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, emerald, mauve
 1. the person who likes mauve is the pakistani##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the dancer##1
 3. the british is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
 5. the pakistani is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 6. the person who likes white is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the dressmaker is the palace house##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the palace house##1
10. the person playing whist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| House      | gothic-revival | palace        | farmhouse |
| Movie-Genre          | comedy    | zombie        | fantasy    |
| Nationality   | colombian        | british        | pakistani    |
| Job           | software-developer        | dressmaker    | dancer   |
| Game         | canasta    | snooker | whist |
| Color     | emerald     | white          | mauve     |

