4. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing go##1
8. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
9. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Birthday         | january    | february     | december            |
| Beverage           | water | 7up | cola |
