 5. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the tower house##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the spanish is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the indonesian##1
10. the modern house is the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Nationality      | spanish    | indonesian     | russian         |
| City          | colone  | nizza    | hamburg         |
| Hobby           | filmmaking | sudoku | cooking          |
| House   | modern    | tower      | townhouse        |
| Cigar   | oliveros     | dunhill     | havana          |
