.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different games are played: whist, backgammon, domino
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, grey, amber
House: art-deco, victorian, ranch-style
City: san-francisco, venice, marseilles
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, airplane, motorbike
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, june, july
1. the victorian house is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who likes brown##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes amber is the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
9. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Game          | backgammon          | domino      | whist      |
| Color         | amber        | grey | brown      |
| House   | art-deco          | victorian        | ranch-style       |
| City   | san-francisco       | venice   | marseilles      |
| Transport           | airplane           | motorbike      | van         |
| Birthday         | july | april    | june |

 